---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 119
By: Mencius
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Suffering Inseparable From the
    Fallen State
---
The fact is that when Heaven proposes to impose a great responsibility on a
man. it is sure first to discipline his purposes by suffering, and his bones
and sinews by bodily toil, to starve his limbs and flesh, to empty his very
self, confounding all his undertakings.
